Jane Carr https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jane_Carr 0 Ellen Jane Carr (born 13 August 1950) is an English actress. She is well known for the voice role of "Pud'n" on the animated The Grim Adventures of Billy and Mandy (US, 2001–2007). She also played a character called "Pudding" in the Jilly Cooper-penned BBC sitcom It's Awfully Bad For Your Eyes, Darling (UK, 1971). Ellen_Jane_Carr ( born 13_August_1950 ) is an_English_actress .
